c: 2
v: 248
t: "Futhi umphrofethi wabo wathi kubona, “ngempela izimpawu zobukhosi bakhe ukuthi kuyofika kunina ibhokisi phakathi kulona kuyobe kunokuthula okuvela eNkosini yenu nokwasalayo okwashiywa umndeni kaMose nomndeni ka-Aroni liyobe lithwelwe yizingelosi ngempela kulokho kunesibonakaliso kunina uma ningabakholwayo"